## ğŸš€ Performance

Benchmarks on typical hardware:
- **Performance Profile**: ~0.9 MB/s, 3 rounds
- **Balanced Profile**: ~0.7 MB/s, 6 rounds  
- **Maximum Profile**: ~0.4 MB/s, 12 rounds

*Performance varies based on hardware and data characteristics*
